2025-09-11 21:58:58 [INFO] Can continue: Well the mourners seemed convinced and they're the<br>experts. Even if it's not though, the sheep are clearly<br>diseased in some way.
2025-09-11 21:58:58 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 21:58:59 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 21:58:59 [INFO] Can continue: Councillor Halgrive
2025-09-11 21:58:59 [INFO] Can continue: As the councillor responsible for public health and safety<br>here in East Ardougne, I am in charge of dealing with<br>this problem.
2025-09-11 21:58:59 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 21:58:59 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 21:58:59 [INFO] Can continue: Councillor Halgrive
2025-09-11 21:58:59 [INFO] Can continue: We need someone to herd these sheep into a safe<br>enclosure, kill them quickly and cleanly and then dispose<br>of the remains hygienically in a special incinerator.
2025-09-11 21:58:59 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-11 21:59:00 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 21:59:00 [INFO] Can continue: Councillor Halgrive
2025-09-11 21:59:00 [INFO] Can continue: Unfortunately, nobody wants to risk catching the plague,<br>and I am unable to find someone willing to undertake<br>this mission for me.
2025-09-11 21:59:00 [INFO] Continue
