2025-09-12 08:21:38 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:21:38 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 08:21:38 [INFO] Can continue: Hi, I hear you finished consecrating Glarial's tomb. Well<br>done.
2025-09-12 08:21:38 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 08:21:39 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:21:39 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 08:21:39 [INFO] Can continue: It was a worthy deed.
2025-09-12 08:21:39 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 08:21:40 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:21:40 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 08:21:40 [INFO] Can continue: Indeed it was. Anyway, are you ready to be taken to<br>Arianwyn?
2025-09-12 08:21:40 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 08:21:42 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:21:42 [INFO] ===
2025-09-12 08:21:42 [INFO] I'm ready.
2025-09-12 08:21:42 [INFO] Not yet.
2025-09-12 08:21:42 [INFO] ===
2025-09-12 08:21:42 [INFO] 1895 Option: 1 I'm ready.
2025-09-12 08:21:44 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:21:44 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 08:21:44 [INFO] Can continue: I'm ready.
2025-09-12 08:21:44 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 08:21:45 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:21:45 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 08:21:45 [INFO] Can continue: Very well. Arianwyn will be in Lletya, I can take you<br>there.
2025-09-12 08:21:45 [INFO] Continue
