2025-09-12 08:29:56 [INFO] Can continue: Gnome on a rack
2025-09-12 08:29:56 [INFO] Can continue: I'm not helping you fix that, as if it hasn't caused<br>enough trouble as it is. Your friends have already tried<br>every torture in the book!
