2025-09-12 08:30:01 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:30:01 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 08:30:01 [INFO] Can continue: How about...<br>feeding you nail and prune stew?
