2025-09-12 08:30:02 [INFO] Can continue: Gnome on a rack
2025-09-12 08:30:02 [INFO] Can continue: That's all I've been living on since I got here.
2025-09-12 08:30:02 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 08:30:04 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:30:04 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 08:30:04 [INFO] Can continue: Set fire to your nostril hair?<br>Let rabid rabbits nibble your toes?<br>Given you a twisted arm?
