2025-09-12 08:30:05 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 08:30:05 [INFO] Can continue: Gnome on a rack
2025-09-12 08:30:05 [INFO] Can continue: Yes, yes and yes.<br>Tried them all, quite liked the toe nibbling.
